body:
I didnt have a match nor am i tilted because of a match but i think this has to be the most toxic game ive ever played in my entire life lmao. Everyone is constantly flaming everyone for the smallest mistakes they make, calling them the N word, a c*nt, a f*g*ot, boosted apes (lmao) its just disgusting. The community is utter trash. I feel like theres no point even playing the game anymore. I wake up wanting to play league only to play a game where someone either feeds/afk's/reports you for no reason/is toxic. Its just a disgusting community and i dont wanna be apart of it. I think im gunna throw in the towel permanently. I like the game but the community has just ruined it. Ive seen so many toxic people get away with racism and stuff. Yet when i tell someone to shut up i seem to get punished for it. Its crazy. Well anyway, what are your thoughts on it ? 

Nice playing with a few of you, the rest of you ruined it for me. Thanks ^^ 
